name: Customizable Shirt Logos
description:
Love your Kickball team? Now, you can get YOUR TEAM LOGO PRINTED on your league approved kickball shirt (or any shirt,) for as little as $10.00 per print with unlimited colors!

Simply place your order and send your logo design to KickballMerchandise@gmail.com

** Orders placed PRIOR to the season start will not include an initial shipping fee from clients within the LA area.**


- Shirt NOT included, this is just for logo printing, you must supply the  
   league approved or regular shirt
- Minimum order of 15 prints
- Direct to Garment Printing
- FULL color printing! (Any and all colors you need!)
- No nasty set-up fees
- The highest quality, washable and durable prints available!
- Send us your print or we can help you create your design
- 9 x 9 logo
